sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant DB

    User->>Frontend: Enter name, email, password
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/users
    Backend->>DB: Check existing user
    alt Email exists
        Backend-->>Frontend: 400 User already exists
        Frontend-->>User: Show error
    else New user
        Backend->>DB: Create user
        DB-->>Backend: User created
        Backend-->>Frontend: 201 Created (JWT token)
        Frontend-->>User: Redirect to Home
    end
